26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_fifo_dmanv17.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:31 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "channv04.h"
30#include "regsnv04.h"
31
32#include <core/client.h>
33#include <core/gpuobj.h>
34#include <subdev/instmem.h>
35
36#include <nvif/class.h>
37#include <nvif/unpack.h>
38
39static int
40nv17_fifo_dma_new(struct nvkm_fifo *base, const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass,
41 void *data, u32 size, struct nvkm_object **pobject)
42{
43 struct nvkm_object *parent = oclass->parent;
44 union {
45 struct nv03_channel_dma_v0 v0;
46 } *args = data;
47 struct nv04_fifo *fifo = nv04_fifo(base);
48 struct nv04_fifo_chan *chan = NULL;
49 struct nvkm_device *device = fifo->base.engine.subdev.device;
50 struct nvkm_instmem *imem = device->imem;
51 int ret;
52
53 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create channel dma size %d\n", size);
54 if (nvif_unpack(args->v0, 0, 0, false)) {
55 nvif_ioctl(parent, "create channel dma vers %d pushbuf %"PRIx64" "
56 "offset %08x\n", args->v0.version,
57 args->v0.pushbuf, args->v0.offset);
58 if (!args->v0.pushbuf)
59 return -EINVAL;
60 } else
61 return ret;
62
63 if (!(chan = kzalloc(sizeof(*chan), GFP_KERNEL)))
64 return -ENOMEM;
65 *pobject = &chan->base.object;
66
67 ret = nvkm_fifo_chan_ctor(&nv04_fifo_dma_func, &fifo->base,
68 0x1000, 0x1000, false, 0, args->v0.pushbuf,
69 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_DMAOBJ) |
70 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_GR) |
71 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_MPEG) | /* NV31- */
72 (1ULL << NVKM_ENGINE_SW),
73 0, 0x800000, 0x10000, oclass, &chan->base);
74 chan->fifo = fifo;
75 if (ret)
76 return ret;
77
78 args->v0.chid = chan->base.chid;
79 chan->ramfc = chan->base.chid * 64;
80
81 nvkm_kmap(imem->ramfc);
82 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x00, args->v0.offset);
83 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x04, args->v0.offset);
84 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x0c, chan->base.push->addr >> 4);
85 nvkm_wo32(imem->ramfc, chan->ramfc + 0x14,
86 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_FETCH_TRIG_128_BYTES |
87 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_FETCH_SIZE_128_BYTES |
88#ifdef __BIG_ENDIAN
89 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_BIG_ENDIAN |
90#endif
91 NV_PFIFO_CACHE1_DMA_FETCH_MAX_REQS_8);
92 nvkm_done(imem->ramfc);
93 return 0;
94}
95
96const struct nvkm_fifo_chan_oclass
97nv17_fifo_dma_oclass = {
98 .base.oclass = NV17_CHANNEL_DMA,
99 .base.minver = 0,
100 .base.maxver = 0,
101 .ctor = nv17_fifo_dma_new,
102};
